  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA34">
<l>aṉṟiv vulaka maḷanta vacaivēko</l>
<l>ṉiṉṟiruntu vēḷukkai nīṇakarvā – yaṉṟu</l>
<l>kiṭantāṉaik kēṭilcī rāṉaimuṉ kañcaik</l>
<l>kaṭantāṉai neñcamē kāṇ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Was there] weariness when he measured this world that day?</l>
<l>Look, heart, at the one who once overcame</l>
<l>Kaṃsa, the one of imperishable glory, the one who that day</l>
<l>stood, sat [and] lay in the large city of Vēḷukkai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
